tinerary leg number this media relates to (5 = Stone Town)\"\n1662\t              },\n1663\t              \"associated_date\": {\n1664\t                \"type\": \"string\",\n1665\t                \"description\": \"Approximate date range, e.g. '2026-08-11/2026-08-13'\"\n1666\t              },\n1667\t              \"tags\": {\n1668\t                \"type\": \"string\",\n1669\t                \"description\": \"Comma-separated tags, e.g. 'stone town,courtyard,architecture'\"\n1670\t              }\n1671\t            }\n1672\t          }\n1673\t        },\n1674\t        {\n1675\t          \"name\": \"park_fees\",\n1676\t          \"schema\": {\n1677\t            \"title\": \"Ngorongoro Conservation Area Tariffs\",\n1678\t            \"description\": \"Official Ngorongoro Conservation Area fees for non-East African visitors extracted from the tariff PDF. Each row captures a fee type, visitor/vehicle category, and USD amount.\",\n1679\t            \"columns\": {\n1680\t              \"id\": {\n1681\t                \"type\": \"string\",\n1682\t                \"description\": \"Primary key\",\n1683\t                \"primaryKey\": true,\n1684\t                \"generated\": \"uuid\"\n1685\t              },\n1686\t              \"fee_type\": {\n1687\t                \"type\": \"string\",\n1688\t                \"description\": \"e.g. Entry Permit, Crater Service, Vehicle Fee, Camping, Safari Crew, Professional Filming\"\n1689\t              },\n1690\t              \"visitor_category\": {\n1691\t                \"type\": \"string\",\n1692\t                \"description\": \"Who this rate applies to, e.g. 'Non-East African adult (16+)', 'Non-East African child 5–16', 'per vehicle', 'per person'\"\n1693\t              },\n1694\t              \"amount_usd\": {\n1695\t                \"type\": \"number\",\n1696\t                \"description\": \"Fee in USD as stated in the official tariff\"\n1697\t              },\n1698\t              \"per_unit\": {\n1699\t                