xpand. Reused in the gallery grid and on the Zanzibar leg detail page.\\' },\\n    { name: \\'DashboardStat\\', purpose: \\'A small summary number-card showing a key figure — next leg in days, pending action-item count, or remaining budget buffer. Reused in the dashboard and as a header strip on key pages.\\' },\\n  ],\\n  pages: [\\n    { route: \\'index\\', purpose: \\'The dashboard home — shows the nearest upcoming itinerary leg (via ItineraryLegCard), pending action-item count (via ActionItemCard), and a budget-at-a-glance with grand total and buffer remaining (via DashboardStat + CostRow). Serves glance-at-dashboard-for-whats-next.\\' },\\n    { route: \\'itinerary\\', purpose: \\'Full chronological itinerary list — all 8 ItineraryLegCards in date order with expandable detail. Serves see-full-itinerary-in-order and anchors navigation to any leg\\\\\\'s notes and photos.\\' },\\n    { route: \\'costs\\', purpose: \\'Complete budget review — all 10 CostRows plus computed total, subtotals, and paid/pending summary. Serves review-all-costs-and-total-budget.\\' },\\n    { route: \\'leg-detail\\', purpose: \\'Deep-dive for one itinerary leg — loads leg data, its linked notes (via notes-by-leg), its photos (if any, via photo-gallery-all filtered by leg), park fees if Ngorongoro, and contact context. Serves check-park-fees-and-rules, resolve-ranger-tip-question, log-bracelet-purchase-and-other-personal-notes, and browse-stone-town-photo-and-gallery.\\' },\\n    { route: \\'gallery\\', purpose: \\'Full photo gallery — all PhotoCards in a grid, with caption and leg link. Serves browse-stone-town-photo-and-gallery and supports future photos.\\' },\\n  ],\\n});'\n---\nIDX 1371 chars 13598\nconst summary -1 \ncurrentTask.resolve 235 'currentTask.resolve({\\n  tables: [\\n    // ---- travelers ----\\n    {\\n      name: \"travelers\",\\n      schema: {\\n        title: \"Travelers\",\\n        description: \"People on the Tanzania trip (Aug 3–20, 2026). Used to contextualize