{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_6XhZo9YzQuT0JSFFqubD7COI","type":"tool_result","content":"plan_app: {\"title\":\"Tanzania Trip 2026 — Kilimanjaro to Zanzibar\",\"purpose\":\"A mobile-first trip companion app to check itinerary, costs, park fees, contacts, personal notes, and a photo gallery for an Aug 3–20, 2026 Tanzania safari + Zanzibar journey.\",\"tables\":[{\"name\":\"travelers\",\"purpose\":\"2 traveler records (Vasilis, Athina Mari) — serves see-contact-info and contextualizes all personal notes and purchases across the trip.\"},{\"name\":\"contacts\",\"purpose\":\"2 contact records — Richard (safari operator/office) and Emmanuel (Ngorongoro driver-guide) — serves see-contact-info and resolve-ranger-tip-question.\"},{\"name\":\"itinerary_legs\",\"purpose\":\"8 chronological legs from Cairo (Aug 3–5) through Zanzibar/Stone Town (Aug 15–20) with date range, nights, hotel, and lodging cost — serves see-full-itinerary-in-order, glance-at-dashboard-for-whats-next, and anchors all leg-tagged notes and photos.\"},{\"name\":\"costs\",\"purpose\":\"10 line-item cost rows with category, amount, status (paid/pending/estimate) — serves review-all-costs-and-total-budget and glance-at-dashboard-for-whats-next.\"},{\"name\":\"park_fees\",\"purpose\":\"2 official Ngorongoro Conservation Area tariff rows from PDF (adult entry permit $70.80/24hrs, crater service fee $295/descent) — serves check-park-fees-and-rules and cross-references costs table.\"},{\"name\":\"voice_memo_notes\",\"purpose\":\"3 notes from the Ngorongoro crater rim recording — driver ID (Emmanuel), bracelet purchase ($20-25/TZS 35,000 for Athina Mari), ranger-tip action item (TZS 5,000 unpaid tip disclosure) — serves resolve-ranger-tip-question and log-bracelet-purchase-and-other-personal-notes.\"},{\"name\":\"photo_gallery\",\"purpose\":\"1 photo row — the Stone Town Zanzibar courtyard image with caption and leg-8 location context — serves browse-stone-town-photo-and-gallery.\"}],\"endpoints\":[{\"route\":\"itinerary-legs-list/GET\",\"purpose\":\"Returns all 8 itinerary legs sorted chronologically with their date ranges, nights, hotel names, and lodging costs for the full-trip list view.\"},{\"route\":\"costs-all/GET\",\"purpose\":\"Returns all 10 cost rows plus computed grand total ($8,217) and subtotals (bulk $6,800 flights+safari, remainder $1,417) for the budget review page.\"},{\"route\":\"park-fees-list/GET\",\"purpose\":\"Returns the 2 official Ngorongoro park-fee tariff rows with cross-reference links to the matching costs table entries (entry permits ×2, service fee).\"},{\"route\":\"contacts-list/GET\",\"purpose\":\"Returns both contact records (Richard and Emmanuel) with their roles and linked action items.\"},{\"route\":\"notes-by-leg/GET\",\"purpose\":\"Returns voice_memo_notes filtered by itinerary leg (e.g. leg 5, Ngorongoro Crater Aug 10–12) plus any user-added notes for log-bracelet-purchase-and-other-personal-notes.\"},{\"route\":\"photo-gallery-all/GET\",\"purpose\":\"Returns the photo gallery rows (starting with the 1 Stone Town courtyard image) linked to their itinerary legs for the gallery and detail views.\"}],\"components\":[{\"name\":\"ItineraryLegCard\",\"purpose\":\"A tappable card showing one itinerary leg: location name, date range, nights count, hotel name, and lodging cost. Expands inline to reveal full details. Reused in the itinerary list and dashboard next-leg preview.\"},{\"name\":\"CostRow\",\"purpose\":\"A compact line-item row showing a cost category, its dollar amount, and a paid/pending/estimate status badge. Reused in the costs full list and the dashboard budget summary.\"},{\"name\":\"ActionItemCard\",\"purpose\":\"A highlighted card for an open to-do: shows the action text (e.g. \\\"Ask Richard about ranger tip — TZS 5,000\\\"), a linked contact, and a tap-to-resolve toggle. Reused on the notes page, the Ngorongoro detail, and the dashboard.\"},{\"name\":\"PhotoCard\",\"purpose\":\"A thumbnail card showing a travel photo with caption, linked leg label, and tap-to-expand. Reused in the gallery grid and on the Zanzibar leg detail page.\"},{\"name\":\"DashboardStat\",\"purpose\":\"A small summary number-card showing a key figure — next leg in days, pending action-item count, or remaining budget buffer. Reused in the dashboard and as a header strip on key pages.\"}],\"pages\":[{\"route\":\"index\",\"purpose\":\"The dashboard home — shows the nearest upcoming itinerary leg (via ItineraryLegCard), pending action-item count (via ActionItemCard), and a budget-at-a-glance with grand total and buffer remaining (via DashboardStat + CostRow). Serves glance-at-dashboard-for-whats-next.\"},{\"route\":\"itinerary\",\"purpose\":\"Full chronological itinerary list — all 8 ItineraryLegCards in date order with expandable detail. Serves see-full-itinerary-in-order and anchors navigation to any leg's notes and photos.\"},{\"route\":\"costs\",\"purpose\":\"Complete budget review — all 10 CostRows plus computed total, subtotals, and paid/pending summary. Serves review-all-costs-and-total-budget.\"},{\"route\":\"leg-detail\",\"purpose\":\"Deep-dive for one itinerary leg — loads leg data, its linked notes (via notes-by-leg), its photos (if any, via photo-gallery-all filtered by leg), park fees if Ngorongoro, and contact context. Serves check-park-fees-and-rules, resolve-ranger-tip-question, log-bracelet-purchase-and-other-personal-notes, and browse-stone-town-photo-and-gallery.\"},{\"route\":\"gallery\",\"purpose\":\"Full photo gallery — all PhotoCards in a grid, with caption and leg link. Serves browse-stone-town-photo-and-gallery and supports future photos.\"}]}\n- read_sources: {\"summary\":\"TANZANIA TRIP APP — COMPLETE BUILD BRIEF (Aug 3–20, 2026)\\n\\nTRAVELERS: Vasilis (primary) + Athina Mari (companion)\\n\\nCONTACTS:\\n- Richard — safari operator / office contact. Quoted the 7-day northern circuit package. Action: ask him about the extra ranger tip (TZS 5,000) before final safari balance payment.\\n- Emmanuel — actual driver-guide at Ngorongoro Crater (not Richard). Skilled spotter; well-regarded.\\n\\nITINERARY (8 legs, spreadsheet rows):\\n1. Cairo (arrival stopover) | Aug 3–5 | 2 nts | Eileen Hotel | $102\\n2. Arusha (pre-safari) | Aug 5–7 | 2 nts | Serengeti Villa | $140\\n3. Tarangire NP | Aug 7–9 | 2 nts | Sangaiwe Tented Camp | $640\\n4. Lake Manyara | Aug 9–10 | 1 nt | Manyara Wildlife Safari Camp | $320\\n5. Ngorongoro Crater | Aug 10–12 | 2 nts | Rhino Lodge | $480\\n6. Serengeti NP (central) | Aug 12–14 | 2 nts | Serengeti Heritage Camp | $720\\n7. Arusha (post-safari) | Aug 14–15 | 1 nt | Serengeti Villa | $70\\n8. Zanzibar / Stone Town | Aug 15–20 | 5 nts | Emerson Spice Hotel | $900\\nTotal lodging: $3,372\\n\\nCOST BREAKDOWN (spreadsheet \\\"costs\\\" sheet — all rows):\\n- International flights (Cairo + Dar return) | $1,800 est | not yet booked (by Mar 2026)\\n- Tanzania e-visa (×2) | $100 | online before departure\\n- Travel insurance (×2) | $80 | World Nomads or similar\\n- Safari package (7-day northern circuit, 2 pax) | $5,000 | quoted by Richard — includes lodging, meals, guide, vehicle\\n- Ngorongoro crater service fee | $295 | PAID (with package deposit)\\n- Ngorongoro entry permits (×2 at $70.80 each) | $142 | payable at gate in cash USD\\n- Tips & gratuities | $150 | guide $10/day, cook $5/day, rangers\\n- Maasai bracelets & souvenirs | $50 | misc cash purchases\\n- Zanzibar activities & meals | $400 | spice tour, snorkeling, dinners\\n- Misc & buffer | $200 | unexpected costs\\n- GRAND TOTAL: $8,217 (flights + safari = $6,800 bulk; remainder $1,417)\\n\\nNGORONGORO OFFICIAL TARIFFS (from PDF):\\n- Non-East African Citizen entry permit (age 16+): $70.80/person/24hrs\\n- Crater service fee (foreign vehicle, per descent): $295\\n- Children 5–16: $23.60; under 5: free\\n\\nVOICE MEMO FACTS (Ngorongoro crater day, recorded at rim):\\n- Driver: Emmanuel (not Richard). Excellent wildlife spotter.\\n- Purchase: two beaded bracelets from a Maasai lady at the crater rim, for Athina Mari. Price paid in Tanzanian shillings, approx $20–25 USD / TZS 35,000.\\n- Hidden fee: Emmanuel disclosed a ranger tip of TZS 5,000 cash sometimes expected at the gate, separate from park fees. User was not informed beforehand.\\n- Open action: ask Richard about the ranger tip before paying the safari balance.\\n\\nPHOTO (stone-town-zanzibar.jpg):\\n- Subject: interior courtyard of a white Mediterranean-style building in Stone Town. Arched windows, dark carved wooden balconies stacked above, photographed from below looking up toward clear blue sky. Warm sunlit walls, ornate balcony railings. Historic travel aesthetic.\\n- Location: Zanzibar / Stone Town (leg 8: Aug 15–20, Emerson Spice Hotel vicinity).\\n\\nPERSONAL NOTES (tanzaniamemories.md):\\n- Confirms travelers, all 8 legs, hotel names, Richard as operator, the Ngorongoro ranger-tip uncertainty, bracelet purchase, and Stone Town courtyard photo.\\n- Vasilis wants a phone-checkable app showing itinerary, costs, park fees, notes, and the photo.\\n\\nREQUIRED APP TABLES (source-derived rows only — no fabrication):\\n- travelers: 2 rows (Vasilis, Athina Mari)\\n- contacts: 2 rows (Richard — operator, Emmanuel — driver-guide)\\n- itinerary_legs: 8 rows exactly as above\\n- costs: 10 rows exactly as above\\n- park_fees: 2 rows (entry permit adult 16+, crater service fee per vehicle)\\n- voice_memo_notes: 3 rows (driver ID, bracelet purchase, ranger-tip action item)\\n- photo_gallery: 1 row (Stone Town courtyard, leg 8, with image reference)\\n\\nEND BRIEF.\",\"ok\":true}\n- user_stories: {\"stories\":[{\"id\":\"see-full-itinerary-in-order\",\"as\":\"the traveller (Vasilis)\",\"want\":\"view the complete 8-leg itinerary chronologically from Aug 3 to Aug 20, 2026\",\"soThat\":\"I can mentally walk through the trip day-by-day and know exactly where I am each night\",\"acceptance\":[\"All 8 legs appear in date order from Cairo (Aug 3–5) through Zanzibar/Stone Town (Aug 15–20)\",\"Each leg shows nights, hotel name, and lodging cost (e.g. Rhino Lodge, 2 nts, $480)\",\"Tap/expand a leg to see its date range and cost without leaving the list view\"]},{\"id\":\"review-all-costs-and-total-budget\",\"as\":\"the traveller\",\"want\":\"review every cost line-item and see the grand total of $8,217\",\"soThat\":\"I know what is paid, what is pending, and how much buffer remains\",\"acceptance\":[","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_0lb5WCKZ0OPAnEXw8oFAxUMW","session_id":"10d74089-d65b-435d-a979-1d29f6775b52","uuid":"8962d311-0cff-4679-a156-3a74d20c9c28","timestamp":"2026-07-16T22:48:00.584Z","subagent_type":"Explore","task_description":"Trace source-data loss"}
