ne Town courtyard, leg 8, with image reference)\\n\\nEND BRIEF.\", \"ok\": true}\nSTART 1342 user_stories fork_129_cb1fd4cd\nSTART 1354 plan_app fork_131_9855ef72\nEND 1364 task_130_0a6b369b {\"title\": \"Tanzania Trip 2026 — Kilimanjaro to Zanzibar\", \"purpose\": \"A mobile-first trip companion app to check itinerary, costs, park fees, contacts, personal notes, and a photo gallery for an Aug 3–20, 2026 Tanzania safari + Zanzibar journey.\", \"tables\": [{\"name\": \"travelers\", \"purpose\": \"2 traveler records (Vasilis, Athina Mari) — serves see-contact-info and contextualizes all personal notes and purchases across the trip.\"}, {\"name\": \"contacts\", \"purpose\": \"2 contact records — Richard (safari operator/office) and Emmanuel (Ngorongoro driver-guide) — serves see-contact-info and resolve-ranger-tip-question.\"}, {\"name\": \"itinerary_legs\", \"purpose\": \"8 chronological legs from Cairo (Aug 3–5) through Zanzibar/Stone Town (Aug 15–20) with date range, nights, hotel, and lodging cost — serves see-full-itinerary-in-order, glance-at-dashboard-for-whats-next, and anchors all leg-tagged notes and photos.\"}, {\"name\": \"costs\", \"purpose\": \"10 line-item cost rows with category, amount, status (paid/pending/estimate) — serves review-all-costs-and-total-budget and glance-at-dashboard-for-whats-next.\"}, {\"name\": \"park_fees\", \"purpose\": \"2 official Ngorongoro Conservation Area tariff rows from PDF (adult entry permit $70.80/24hrs, crater service fee $295/descent) — serves check-park-fees-and-rules and cross-references costs table.\"}, {\"name\": \"voice_memo_notes\", \"purpose\": \"3 notes from the Ngorongoro crater rim recording — driver ID (Emmanuel), bracelet purchase ($20-25/TZS 35,000 for Athina Mari), ranger-tip action item (TZS 5,000 unpaid tip disclosure) — serves resolve-ranger-tip-question and log-bracelet-purchase-and-other-personal-notes.\"}, {\"name\": \"photo_gallery\", \"purpose\": \"1 photo row — the Stone Town Zanzibar courtyard image with caption and leg-8 location context — serves browse-stone-town-photo-and-gallery.\"}], \"endpoints\": [{\"route\": \"itinerary-legs-list/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns all 8 itinerary legs sorted chronologically with their date ranges, nights, hotel names, and lodging costs for the full-trip list view.\"}, {\"route\": \"costs-all/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns all 10 cost rows plus computed grand total ($8,217) and subtotals (bulk $6,800 flights+safari, remainder $1,417) for the budget review page.\"}, {\"route\": \"park-fees-list/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns the 2 official Ngorongoro park-fee tariff rows with cross-reference links to the matching costs table entries (entry permits ×2, service fee).\"}, {\"route\": \"contacts-list/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns both contact records (Richard and Emmanuel) with their roles and linked action items.\"}, {\"route\": \"notes-by-leg/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns voice_memo_notes filtered by itinerary leg (e.g. leg 5, Ngorongoro Crater Aug 10–12) plus any user-added notes for log-bracelet-purchase-and-other-personal-notes.\"}, {\"route\": \"photo-gallery-all/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns the photo gallery rows (starting with the 1 Stone Town courtyard image) linked to their itinerary legs for the gallery and detail views.\"}], \"components\": [{\"name\": \"ItineraryLegCard\", \"purpose\": \"A tappable card showing one itinerary leg: location name, date range, nights count, hotel name, and lodging cost. Expands inline to reveal full details. Reused in the itinerary list and dashboard next-leg preview.\"}, {\"name\": \"CostRow\", \"purpose\": \"A compact line-item row showing a cost category, its dollar amount, and a paid/pending/estimate status badge. Reused in the costs full list and the dashboard budget summary.\"}, {\"name\": \"ActionItemCard\", \"purpose\": \"A highlighted card for an open to-do: shows the action text (e.g. \\\"Ask Richard about ranger tip — TZS 5,000\\\"), a linked contact, and a tap-to-resolve toggle. Reused on the notes page, the Ngorongoro detail, and the dashboard.\"}, {\"name\": \"PhotoCard\", \"purpose\": \"A thumbnail card showing a travel photo with caption, linked leg label, and tap-to-expand. Reused in the gallery grid and on the Zanzibar leg detail page.\"}, {\"name\": \"DashboardStat\", \"purpose\": \"A small summary number-card showing a key figure — next leg in days, pending action-item count, or remaining budget buffer. Reused in the dashboard and as a header strip on key pages.\"}], \"pages\": [{\"route\": \"index\", \"purpose\": \"The dashboard home — shows the nearest upcoming itinerary leg (via ItineraryLegCard), pending action-item count (via ActionItemCard), and a budget-at-a-glance with grand total and buffer remaining (via DashboardStat + CostRow). Serves glance-at-dashboard-for-whats-next.\"}, {\"route\": \"itinerary\", \"purpose\": \"Full chronological itinerary list — all 8 ItineraryLegCards in date order with expandable detail. Serves see-full-itinerary-in-order and anchors navigation to any leg's notes and photos.\"}, {\"route\": \"costs\", \"purpose\": \"Complete budget review — all 10 CostRows plus computed total, subtotals, and paid/pending summary. Serves review-all-costs-and-total-budget.\"}, {\"route\": \"leg-detail\", \"purpose\": \"Deep-dive for one itinerary leg — loads leg data, its linked notes (via notes-by-leg), its photos (if any, via photo-gallery-all filtered by leg), park fees if Ngorongoro, and contact context. Serves check-park-fees-and-rules, resolve-ranger-tip-question, log-bracelet-purchase-and-other-personal-notes, and browse-stone-town-photo-and-gallery.\"}, {\"route\": \"gallery\", \"purpose\": \"Full photo gallery — all PhotoCards in a grid, with caption and leg link. Serves browse-stone-town-photo-and-gallery and supports future photos.\"}]}\nSTART 1366 plan_tables fork_133_921a1b93\nEND 1376 task_132_f78a8006 {\"tables\": [{\"name\": \"travelers\", \"schema\": {\"title\": \"Travelers\", \"description\"