rched windows, dark wooden balconies, decorative railings, classic Zanzibar architecture). Serves: see-zanzibar-stone-town-photo.\"}, {\"name\": \"action_items\", \"purpose\": \"Pending to-dos and uncertainties — confirm ranger tip with Richard, pay safari balance $960 cash, verify bracelet cost, confirm Zanzibar insurance details, Pesapal 5% surcharge note. Serves: check-action-items.\"}, {\"name\": \"contacts\", \"purpose\": \"Key people and organisations — Richard (Suricata Safaris), Emmanuel (driver-guide), each hotel, The Rock Restaurant, embassy reference — with phone, email, and role. Serves: access-key-contacts, view-trip-overview.\"}, {\"name\": \"practical_notes\", \"purpose\": \"Packing and logistics tips — soft bags for safari, Decathlon Forclaz trekking line, DEET repellent, Zanzibar driving permit info, north-coast swimming advice, Tanzania e-visa requirement, August peak-season note. Serves: see-practical-notes.\"}], \"endpoints\": [{\"route\": \"trip-overview/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns the singleton trip record with route summary, travellers, dates, and rolled-up cost totals for the home dashboard.\"}, {\"route\": \"itinerary-days/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns all 18 day rows (Aug 3–20) in chronological order with linked accommodation, flight, and activity refs.\"}, {\"route\": \"flights/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns all 6 flight legs with airline, flight numbers, times, origin/destination, and booking references.\"}, {\"route\": \"accommodations/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns all 8 accommodations in chronological order with address, contact, dates, nights, and cost.\"}, {\"route\": \"costs/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns every cost line item with amount, currency, payment status, and notes — grouped by category.\"}, {\"route\": \"ngorongoro-fees/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns Ngorongoro Conservation Area tariff table rows — entry permits, crater service fee, vehicle fees, and separate Olduvai/Laetoli fees.\"}, {\"route\": \"safari-notes/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns voice-memo crater-day notes — driver-guide details, bracelet purchase, unconfirmed ranger tip.\"}, {\"route\": \"stone-town-photo/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns the Stone Town courtyard photo reference and architecture description.\"}, {\"route\": \"action-items/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns all pending action items and uncertainties with status flags.\"}, {\"route\": \"contacts/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns all key contacts with phone, email, role, and notes.\"}, {\"route\": \"practical-notes/GET\", \"purpose\": \"Returns all practical trip notes — packing, permits, swimming, visa, peak-season.\"}], \"components\": [{\"name\": \"TripHeroCard\", \"purpose\": \"Reusable card for the home dashboard hero — trip title, travellers, date range, route badges, and total-cost summary. Used on index page and trip-overview page.\"}, {\"name\": \"DayTimelineRow\", \"purpose\": \"Single day row for the chronological itinerary timeline — date badge, day title, accommodation icon, activity summary, meal flags. Repeats for all 18 days on the itinerary list page and the home mini-timeline.\"}, {\"name\": \"FlightCard\", \"purpose\": \"Card showing a single flight leg — airline logo area, flight number, origin→destination, departure/arrival times, booking ref. Repeats for 6 legs.\"}, {\"name\": \"AccommodationCard\", \"purpose\": \"Card for one accommodation — name, date range, nights count, address, phone, email, cost badge. Repeats for 8 accommodations.\"}, {\"name\": \"CostLineItem\", \"purpose\": \"A single cost row — label, amount, currency icon, paid/due/unconfirmed status pill. Repeats for every cost entry on the costs list page.\"}, {\"name\": \"FeeTariffRow\", \"purpose\": \"Tariff table row — fee name, visitor category, TZS amount, USD amount, notes. Repeats for Ngorongoro fee entries.\"}, {\"name\": \"ActionItemChip\", \"purpose\": \"Pending-action chip with status colour (unconfirmed/urgent/due) — label, description, and a link to the relevant contact. Rep