. WALKING SAFARI GUIDE FEES\n\n| Category | Tanzanian (TZS) | Non-EA (USD) |\n|---|---|---|\n| Short walks (1–4 hrs), adults | TZS 11,800 | $23.60 |\n| Short walks, children (12–16 yrs) | TZS 5,900 | $11.80 |\n| Long walks (above 4 hrs), adults | TZS 23,600 | $29.50 |\n| Long walks, children | TZS 11,800 | $17.70 |\n| Endoro Nature Trail & Elephant Caves, adult | TZS 11,800 | $17.70 |\n| Endoro Nature Trail & Elephant Caves, child | TZS 5,900 | $11.80 |\n\n### G. PERMIT FEE FOR SERVING HOT LUNCH (Bush Lunch) — $11.80 per person, Non-EA; TZS 5,900 per Tanzanian\n\n### H. LANDING FEES FOR AIRCRAFT\n\n| Aircraft Category | Local Registered (TZS) | Foreign Registered (USD) |\n|---|---|---|\n| Up to 4 Seater — Private | TZS 11,800 | $59.00 |\n| Up to 4 Seater — Commercial | TZS 17,700 | $141.60 |\n| 5–12 Seater — Private | TZS 17,700 | $141.60 |\n| 5–12 Seater — Commercial | TZS 23,600 | $200.60 |\n| 13–20 Seater — Private | TZS 23,600 | $200.60 |\n| 13–20 Seater — Commercial | TZS 41,300 | $377.60 |\n| Over 20 Seater — Private | TZS 59,000 | N/A |\n| Over 20 Seater — Commercial | TZS 70,800 | N/A |\n\n### I. OLDUVAI GORGE / SHIFTING SAND / LAETOLI FOOTPRINTS\n\n| Age Group | East African (TZS) | Non-East African (USD) |\n|---|---|---|\n| 16 years and above | TZS 35,400 | $35.40 |\n| 5 to 16 years | TZS 11,800 | $11.80 |\n| Below 5 years | Free | Free |\n\n### J. HOT AIR BALLOON SAFARIS\n\n| Age Group | East African (TZS) | Non-East African (USD) |\n|---|---|---|\n| 8 years and above | TZS 47,200 | $39.53 |\n| Below 8 years | TZS 11,800 | N/A |\n\n### K. HORSE RIDING SAFARIS (per person)\n\n| Age Group | East African (TZS) | Non-East African (USD) |\n|---|---|---|\n| 16 years and above | TZS 11,800 | $17.70 |\n| Below 16 years | TZS 11,800 | $11.80 |\n\n### L. MOUNTAIN BIKING (per person)\n\n| Age Group | East African (TZS) | Non-East African (USD) |\n|---|---|---|\n| 16 years and above | TZS 5,900 | $5.90 |\n| 5 to 16 years | TZS 2,360 | $2.36 |\n| Below 5 years | Free | Free |\n\n### M. SUNDOWN FEE\n\n| Age Group | East African (TZS) | Non-East African (USD) |\n|---|---|---|\n| 16 years and above | TZS 35,400 | $59.00 |\n| 5 to 16 years | TZS 11,800 | $11.80 |\n| Below 5 years | Free | Free |\n\n### N. CONCESSION FEE — for lodges and permanent tented camps (rates on application)\n\n### O. FILMING / PHOTOGRAPHIC FEES — $354.00 per crew member per day (excludes crater service & vehicle fees)\n\n### P. PENALTIES & FINES\n- Over-speeding: TZS 118,000 per vehicle\n- Fraud: normal fee + 100% penalty\n- Off-road driving / wrong parking / prohibited actions: TZS 118,000\n\n### Key Conditions & Rules\n- Permit valid for **one entry within 24 hours only**; single entry for all permits including crater service\n- **Tariffs subject to change without notice**\n- Only 4×4 vehicles up to 3,500 kg tare weight allowed on Crater floor\n- Driving hours: 06:00–18:00; crater descent gates close at 16:00, exit by 18:00\n- Speed limits: 50 kph in the area, 25 kph at the crater\n- Maximum 5 vehicles at an animal sighting; keep 25 m distance\n- Off-road driving prohibited; no plastic bags allowed\n- Walking safaris must be accompanied by an armed NCAA ranger\n- Licensed guide mandatory for all crater visitors\n- Photography of locals prohibited except in designated Cultural Bomas\nSEQ 1521 task_143_21a6096c\nBUILD BRIEF — Vasilis & Athina Mari Tanzania Trip, Aug 3–20 2026\n\nCONTACTS:\n- Richard — safari company office contact (company undisclosed in sources)\n- Emmanuel — driver/guide, separate from Richard, knowledgeable about Ngorongoro\n\nFLIGHTS (from tanzaniamemories.md + trip-costs.xlsx sheet:flights):\n- Outbound: Cairo → Arusha (Aug 5), onward via Precision Air or similar\n- Zanzibar → Dar es Salaam (Aug 18), then Dar es Salaam → home (Aug 19–20)\n- Flight costs in spreadsheet\n\nACCOMMODATION (from trip-costs.xlsx sheet:legs):\n1. Cairo arrival stopover: Eileen Hotel, Aug 3–5, 2 nights, $102\n2. Arusha pre-safari: Serengeti Villa, Aug 5–7, 2 ni